1
00:00:09,100 --> 00:00:14,900
=The Reincarnated Lovers=

2
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:16,500
=Episode 12=

3
00:00:21,679 --> 00:00:22,519
(Qing'an.)

4
00:00:50,960 --> 00:00:52,039
Is this how

5
00:00:52,799 --> 00:00:54,200
the Prince of Jiangling

6
00:00:55,039 --> 00:00:56,320
treats his savior?

7
00:00:57,330 --> 00:00:59,280
Baiye Pavilion's
newly appointed pavilion master.

8
00:01:00,119 --> 00:01:01,240
Young Master Hanya.

9
00:01:02,399 --> 00:01:03,159
Nice to meet you.

10
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:05,000
Sigh.

11
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:06,879
Indeed,

12
00:01:07,719 --> 00:01:08,799
nothing can escape

13
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,000
Prince of Jiangling.

14
00:01:11,239 --> 00:01:12,400
Master of Baiye Pavilion.

15
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:15,000
Why were you in the woods today?

16
00:01:15,799 --> 00:01:16,560
Just passing by.

17
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:17,799
A coincidence.

18
00:01:18,519 --> 00:01:21,159
I was just on my way
to the Prince of Jiangling's residence.

19
00:01:27,610 --> 00:01:29,000
To seek refuge with Your Highness.

20
00:01:31,210 --> 00:01:31,799
Your Highness.

21
00:01:32,159 --> 00:01:33,079
Young Master Hanya

22
00:01:33,500 --> 00:01:35,490
has pledged allegiance to you
with Baiye Pavilion.

23
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,239
Your Highness.

24
00:01:36,519 --> 00:01:38,159
You truly win everyone's hearts.

25
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:40,280
Zhu Que.

26
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:42,680
What do you think of this?

27
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:44,519
Is there any problem?

28
00:01:44,850 --> 00:01:47,280
Baiye Pavilion is the top
assassin organization in the world.

29
00:01:47,500 --> 00:01:48,820
Whoever possesses this Baiye Token

30
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:51,480
can command all the assassins
of Baiye Pavilion.

31
00:01:52,079 --> 00:01:53,120
Young Master Hanya

32
00:01:53,519 --> 00:01:56,079
entrusting such a pivotal item to you

33
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:56,920
must signify

34
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,280
a sincere act of allegiance.

35
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,879
But there's something about him.

36
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,799
A familiar aura.

37
00:02:17,650 --> 00:02:19,199
Thank you for saving me, Young Master.

38
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,439
My pleasure, Your Highness.

39
00:02:24,439 --> 00:02:25,080
Your Highness?

40
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:28,960
Your eyes are truly beautiful.

41
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,080
Very much like

42
00:02:31,639 --> 00:02:32,599
someone I used to know.

43
00:02:34,639 --> 00:02:36,520
But what happened to your hair?

44
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:40,000
When I was young,
I contracted a strange illness.

45
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,840
My head of black hair

46
00:02:42,159 --> 00:02:43,840
suddenly turned white.

47
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:46,479
My body is no longer what it used to be.

48
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,080
Indeed,

49
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,439
it's quite lamentable.

50
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:52,919
Your Highness.

51
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,479
You don't need to comfort me.

52
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,039
I actually think

53
00:02:57,319 --> 00:02:58,400
that I am fortunate.

54
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:01,560
If I still had my former looks,

55
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,520
I would have countless pursuers.

56
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,719
In this world,

57
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,560
love

58
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:11,599
is the hardest thing to understand.

59
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,960
Young Master Hanya, you're humorous.

60
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:23,520
Looks like my wife
has become more cheerful lately.

61
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:25,319
Even with a stranger,

62
00:03:26,159 --> 00:03:27,400
she can chat away freely.

63
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,240
Young Master Hanya is our savior.

64
00:03:30,759 --> 00:03:32,000
How is he a stranger?

65
00:03:46,919 --> 00:03:49,199
Young Master Hanya,
you're truly likable.

66
00:03:49,759 --> 00:03:51,120
Even my mother

67
00:03:51,599 --> 00:03:53,080
admires you at first sight.

68
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,400
She wants you as her godson.

69
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,039
I wonder,

70
00:03:57,479 --> 00:03:58,800
how do you feel about that?

71
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,840
To refuse would be impolite.

72
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,840
Mother.

73
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:08,280
Please have some tea.

74
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,039
Uncanny.

75
00:04:12,439 --> 00:04:14,000
The resemblance is uncanny.

76
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:17,839
Say,

77
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:19,879
isn't it as if

78
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,920
the heavens have arranged

79
00:04:23,319 --> 00:04:25,399
for me to lose one son

80
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,920
and gain another son.

81
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:32,759
Mother.

82
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,240
You are a good person.

83
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,100
You will surely
have the protection of the heavens.

84
00:04:38,399 --> 00:04:39,519
Good child.

85
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:40,959
From now on,

86
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:42,560
we are a family.

87
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,439
Xuanyi.

88
00:04:45,439 --> 00:04:47,600
Take good care of your younger brother.

89
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:49,680
Yes.

90
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:50,839
Mother.

91
00:04:56,199 --> 00:04:56,879
Brother.

92
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:01,519
Sister-in-law.

93
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,600
Try these, everyone.

94
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:12,639
These

95
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:13,879
are all made by Jingyue.

96
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,439
Her culinary skills

97
00:05:15,759 --> 00:05:16,920
are extraordinary.

98
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:18,480
Your Highness.

99
00:05:18,639 --> 00:05:19,600
You're teasing me.

100
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:22,000
I'm just telling the truth.

101
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:23,680
Jingyue

102
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,800
is indeed our lucky star.

103
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:29,199
Unlike someone

104
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:32,319
who encountered assassins
on her way home

105
00:05:33,839 --> 00:05:35,040
and implicated others.

106
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,439
How unlucky.

107
00:05:37,759 --> 00:05:39,000
As the Prince of Jiangling,

108
00:05:39,439 --> 00:05:40,519
