111
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:44,240
are too many to count.

112
00:05:45,010 --> 00:05:46,290
I've long been accustomed to it.

113
00:05:48,879 --> 00:05:49,199
Here.

114
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:50,600
Thank you.

115
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,639
I'm really sorry.

116
00:05:54,839 --> 00:05:55,759
Are you okay?

117
00:05:56,399 --> 00:05:57,199
It's okay, Wanwan.

118
00:05:57,879 --> 00:05:59,240
It's my carelessness.

119
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,800
Hurting the Princess

120
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:02,639
deserves a good slap.

121
00:06:04,439 --> 00:06:05,240
I dare you.

122
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,319
Mother, what are you doing?

123
00:06:17,839 --> 00:06:19,240
It's just a trivial matter.

124
00:06:19,279 --> 00:06:20,439
Please stay calm, Mother.

125
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,199
Do you still remember

126
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,199
who killed Qing'an?

127
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:28,720
Who caused him to be buried
without proper rites?

128
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:32,480
