blaming all these sins on my wife

129
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:34,439
seems unfair, isn't it?

130
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,560
Fine.

131
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,839
I'm old now.

132
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:48,120
I can't control you anymore.

133
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,040
Your Highness.

134
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:53,199
Calm down.

135
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:56,120
Young Master Qing'an, in his afterlife,

136
00:06:56,530 --> 00:06:57,920
would find it hard to rest in peace

137
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,260
if you worry so much about him.

138
00:07:07,450 --> 00:07:09,390
(It is said
that tying a white ribbon on a willow)

139
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,079
(can bring blessings to the departed.)

140
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,759
(Qing'an.)

141
00:07:12,759 --> 00:07:14,990
(May you be free from illness
and disaster in the next life.)

142
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,800
Your Highness.

143
00:07:29,319 --> 00:07:30,399
Young Master Hanya.

144
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,040
Your Highness.

145
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,160
May I

146
00:07:35,079 --> 00:07:36,199
have a word with you?

147
00:07:36,639 --> 00:07:36,959
Sure.

148
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,000
Your Highness.

149
00:07:50,279 --> 00:07:51,800
I apologize for my abruptness earlier.

150
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,040
No, I was too focused.

151
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,279
May I know

152
00:07:58,279 --> 00:07:59,160
who Your Highness

153
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:01,600
was commemorating?

154
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,360
He was someone from my past.

155
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:08,560
He might not be a relative,

156
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,759
but he was more than that.

157
00:08:10,959 --> 00:08:12,279
We grew up since childhood,

158
00:08:12,959 --> 00:08:14,360
and he treated me very well.

159
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:17,639
But I

160
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:19,920
brought him harm.

161
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,759
(Both in the past life and the present.)

162
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:24,560
That's not your fault.

163
00:08:27,839 --> 00:08:28,879
I meant,

164
00:08:29,759 --> 00:08:31,399
if what you said is true,

165
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,159
that you two had a deep bond,

166
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,759
then he surely wouldn't blame you.

167
00:08:37,279 --> 00:08:38,399
If not for me,

168
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:41,100
